Nathan Bent, son of the former Big Brother Naija season six housemate, Jackie Bent, popularly known as Jackie B, has called her out for twerking on social media. The 10-year-old boy in a video which was posted by his mother on Instagram, stated during a conversation that she is embarrassing mankind for twerking. She asked in the video after twerking, “Am I embarrassing you? What is the problem? ” And he answered, “No, you are embarrassing every mankind.”